of%20energy.%20Truck%20drivers%20use%20them%20for%20endurance%2C%20gym%20bros%20pop%20them%20before%20a%20workout%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchuck-schumer-nicotine-zyn-republican-right-wing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETucker%20Carlson%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20can%20%26quot%3Bfree%20your%20mind.%26quot%3B%20Carlson%2C%20who%20says%20he%20uses%20Zyn%20every%20second%20he's%20awake%2C%20also%20claimed%20(incorrectly)%20that%20Zyn%20improves%20sexual%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Zyn%20users%20are%20buzzing%20about%20another%20purported%20side%20effect%3A%20Some%20claim%20that%20their%20habit%20has%20triggered%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrea%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%2C%20author%20of%20consumer%20trend%20newsletter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snaxshot.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnaxshot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pointed%20out%20this%20craze%20this%20week%2C%20sharing%20a%20collection%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20about%20Zyn%20and%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20boy's%20down%20like%2030%20pounds%20in%20a%20month.%20O-Zyn-pic.%20It%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Instagram%20user%2C%20who%20runs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC456a4su9VY%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20popular%20golfing%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20in%20one%20of%20the%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiet%20pages%20on%20Reddit%20are%20filling%20up%20with%20Zyn%20chatter%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BI've%20used%20Zyn%20nicotine%20pouches%20occasionally%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20but%20have%20started%20to%20use%20them%20regularly%20because%20they%20help%20me%20focus%20and%20curb%20my%20hunger%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Reddit%20user%20wrote%20in%20r%2Fintermittentfasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20history%20has%20taught%20us%20anything%2C%20it's%20that%20nicotine%20products%20do%20suppress%20appetite%20somewhat%20and%20they%20will%20be%20used%20for%20weight%20loss.%20Plus%2C%20there's%20high%20demand%20for%20a%20quick%20and%20inexpensive%20hack%20to%20replace%20new%20blockbuster%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20which%20are%20currently%20in%20shortage%2C%20causing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F05%2F16%2Fweight-loss-drug-shortage-wegovy-ozempic%3Futm_source%3Dnewsletter%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_campaign%3Dnewsletter_axiosvitals%26stream%3Dtop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidespread%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Carolyn%20Bramante%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%2C%20said%20while%20it%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20sense%26quot%3B%20that%20people%20are%20trying%20this%20out%2C%20she%20has%20concerns%20about%20the%20unknown%20potential%20effects%20of%20nicotine%20pouches%20on%20a%20person's%20heart%20and%20blood%20vessels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicotine%20may%20trigger%20inflammation%20of%20the%20molecules%20that%20fat%20cells%20release.%20None%20of%20this%20is%20well-studied%2C%20Bramante%2C%20who%20works%20in%20adult%20and%20pediatric%20weight%20management%20clinics%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20FDA-approved%20treatments%20for%20obesity%20now.%20It's%20important%20to%20think%20about%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d94c1c49-592e-472d-a831-5ca2a1468563%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20years%2C%20nicotine%20was%20marketed%20as%20a%20feminine%20diet%20hack.%20Now%2C%20it's%20for%20men.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22738%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22old%20ad%20for%20lucky%20strikes%20%26quot%3Blight%20a%20lucky%20and%20you'll%20never%20mess%20sweets%20that%20make%20you%20fat%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66467f749fc063e829b2126c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20actual%201920s%20ad%20for%20Lucky%20Strike%20cigarettes.%3Cp%3EBettmann%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201920s%2C%20Lucky%20Strike%20cigarettes%20were%20marketed%20as%20a%20healthier%2C%20less%20%26quot%3Bfattening%26quot%3B%20alternative%20to%20candy%2C%20helping%20smokers%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20a%20slender%20figure.%26quot%3B%20It's%20an%20idea%20that%20persisted%20in%20cigarette%20ads%20for%20the%20next%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftobacco.stanford.edu%2Fcigarettes%2Fkeeps-you-slim%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E50%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govinfo.gov%2Fcontent%2Fpkg%2FSTATUTE-79%2Fpdf%2FSTATUTE-79-Pg282.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregulations%3C%2Fa%3E%20introduced%20in%20the%2060s%20to%20block%20tobacco%20companies%20from%20advertising%20cigarettes%20as%20slimming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20e-cigarettes%20and%20vapes%20came%20on%20the%20scene%20it%20was%20no%20different.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2014%2F03%2F03%2F284006424%2Fe-cigarette-critics-worry-new-ads-will-make-vaping-cool-for-kids%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2014%20ad%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Sports%20Illustrated's%20swimsuit%20issue%20has%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20beach%20wearing%20a%20tiny%20triangle%20bottom%2C%20promoting%20Blu%20e-cigarettes%20as%20%26quot%3BSlim.%20Charged.%20Ready%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZyn%20is%20different.%20It%20is%20not%20marketed%20as%20slimming%20or%20feminine.%20Its%20branding%20is%20simple%20and%20masculine.%20And%20it's%20gamified%3A%20When%20you%20buy%20a%20can%20of%2015%20pouches%20for%20%244.90%20%E2%80%94%20in%20flavors%20like%20citrus%2C%20smooth%2C%20and%20chill%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20generate%20points.%205630%20points%20earns%20you%20a%20pair%20of%20Apple%20AirPods%2C%209000%20points%20earns%20you%20a%20Samsung%20TV%2C%208650%20points%20earns%20you%20a%20pizza%20oven.%20You%20get%2015%20points%20per%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20marketing%20ploy%20by%20Philip%20Morris%2C%20which%20owns%20Zyn.%20It%20is%20Zyn%20%3Cem%3Eusers%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20are%20driving%20the%20narrative%20of%20these%20pouches%20as%20a%20diet%20hack%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20cheat%20code%20you%20can%20unlock%20if%20you%20buy%20in.%20Forget%20a%20Sonos%20sound%20system%2C%20what%20about%20losing%20that%20belly%20weight%20you%20can't%20seem%20to%20shift%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%E2%80%A6%20'this%20is%20something%20that%20I%20can%20literally%20buy%20in%20a%20gas%20station%2C%20that%20I'm%20still%20getting%20points%20on%2C%20that%20has%20this%20byproduct%20effect%20that%20it%20wasn't%20intended%20for%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%2C%20who%20has%20been%20watching%20this%20trend%20bubble%20up%20for%20years%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-celebrities-denied-semaglutide-wegovy-weight-loss-drugs-khloe-kardashian-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emale%20celebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Elon%20Musk%2C%20Charles%20Barkley)%20have%20reported%20dramatic%20weight-loss%20after%20taking%20GLP-1%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20and%20Mounjaro.%20But%20those%20drugs%20cost%20over%20%241%2C000%20for%20one%20month's%20supply%2C%20and%20are%20incredibly%20hard%20to%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20I%20said%20it's%20the%20Ozempic%20for%20the%20masses%2C%26quot%3B%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20said%2C%20jokingly.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20people%20can't%20afford%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20talk%20about.%20This%20feels%20like%20a%20discreet%20way%20to%20lose%20weight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7bbb663-333e-45bf-80a7-3fcc53e65cdb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EZyn%20may%20suppress%20appetite%20short-term%20but%20the%20collateral%20damage%20is%20huge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22zyn%20flip%20can%20with%20pouches%20inside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66467fd014fb5b23cc5d7f32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20suspect%20the%20reason%20nicotine%20works%20as%20a%20mild%20appetite%20suppressant%20is%20because%20it%20activates%20neurons%20in%20the%20brain%20that%20control%20hunger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20because%20Zyn%20users%20absorb%20more%20nicotine%20than%20cigarette%20smokers%2C%20the%20appetite-suppressing%20effect%20of%20popping%20a%20Zyn%20pouch%20in%20your%20gumline%20might%20be%20even%20greater%20than%20lighting%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20even%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell-reports%2Ffulltext%2FS2211-1247(23)00477-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20recent%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20(in%20mice)%20combining%20Ozempic%20and%20nicotine%20together%20to%20produce%20a%20greater%20weight%20loss%20effect%2C%20Dr.%20Beverly%20Tchang%2C%20an%20endocrinologist%20at%20Weill-Cornell's%20comprehensive%20weight%20control%20center%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said.%20But%2C%20Tchang%20emphasized%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20people%20should%20use%20nicotine%20as%20a%20weight%20loss%20aid.%20We%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mountsinai.org%2Fhealth-library%2Fpoison%2Fnicotine-poisoning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoxic%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20might%20be%20for%20people%2C%20nor%20what%20a%20proper%20dose%20might%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOzempic%20boosts%20the%20action%20of%20a%20hormone%20we%20produce%20naturally%20in%20our%20gut.%20That's%20how%20it%20helps%20people%20feel%20full%20quickly%2C%20and%20manage%20blood%20sugar.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20like%20hormone%20replacement%20for%20people%20who%20have%20low%20levels%20of%20GLP-1%2C%26quot%3B%20Bramante%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20GLP1%20injection%20pen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664680b49fc063e829b212d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EIuliia%20Burmistrova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENicotine%20isn't%20like%20a%20hormone.%20It's%20an%20addictive%20stimulant%2C%20and%20one%20that%20(unlike%20Ozempic)%20has%20not%20been%20studied%20in%20randomized%2C%20controlled%20trials%2C%20to%20evaluate%20safety%20and%20efficacy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20nicotine%20pouches%20circumvent%20the%20health%20effects%20of%20cigarettes%20that%20are%20caused%20by%20tobacco%2C%20they%20still%20do%20a%20number%20on%20your%20body.%20They're%20highly%20addictive%2C%20and%20bump%20up%20your%20blood%20pressure.%20This%20gives%20Bramante%20pause.%20She%20worries%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20don't%20fully%20understand%20how%20nicotine%20works%20to%20regulate%20appetite%20in%20people%2C%20specifically%20with%20obesity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflammation%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20cardiovascular%20issues%20are%20all%20at%20play%20when%20people%20carry%20around%20excess%20weight%2C%20and%20popping%20a%20Zyn%20could%20tip%20the%20scales%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBramante%20is%20especially%20concerned%20about%20people%20with%20obesity%20trying%20nicotine%20out%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20because%20it%20could%20increase%20the%20amount%20of%20inflammatory%20molecules%20that%20fat%20cells%20release%20(leptin).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20advise%20them%20to%20seek%20care%20for%20obesity%20treatment%20from%20their%20primary%20care%20clinician%20and%2For%20an%20obesity%20medicine%20specialist%2C%20with%20the%20mindset%20that%20it's%20a%20long-term%20relationship%20with%20follow-up%20and%20with%20multiple%20treatment%20options%20that%20we%20can%20now%20adjust%20to%20meet%20an%20individual's%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhilip%20Morris%20International%20and%20its%20affiliates%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Swedish%20Match%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20ZYN%20%E2%80%94%20fully%20meet%20and%20exceed%20the%20regulations%20governing%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Philip%20Morris%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20response%20to%20BI's%20previous%20reporting%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-pouches-what-are-nicotine-does-to-heart-body-brain-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20effects%20of%20Zyn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-nicotine-weight-loss-ozempic-health-risk-masculinity-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715939101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66467d6720abc1efe8facfdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-nicotine-weight-loss-ozempic-health-risk-masculinity-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20are%20calling%20Zyn%20nicotine%20pouches%20O-Zyn-pic.%20But%20experts%20say%20using%20nicotine%20for%20weight%20loss%20is%20a%20potentially%20risky%20idea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mdegraaf%40businessinsider.com%20(Mia%20de%20Graaf%2CHilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-nicotine-weight-loss-ozempic-health-risk-masculinity-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MEA%20issues%20advisory%20for%20Indians%20travelling%20to%20Laos%2C%20Cambodia%20for%20jobs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715939055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110205149%2Cimgsize-1498265.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmea-issues-advisory-for-indians-travelling-to-laos-cambodia-for-jobs%2Farticleshow%2F110204801.cms%22%2C%22