on%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20called%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20secretary%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20but%20couldn't%20get%20through%2C%20after%20which%20she%20sent%20him%20a%20WhatsApp%20text%20but%20did%20not%20get%20a%20response.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwati%20Maliwal%20says%20she%20went%20inside%20the%20residential%20area%20through%20the%20main%20door%20of%20the%20chief%20minister's%20house%2C%20as%20she%20had%20always%20done%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20since%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20was%20not%20present.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20AAP%20MP%20informed%20the%20staff%20present%20there%20to%20tell%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20that%20she%20was%20there%20to%20meet%20him%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20was%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20present%20in%20the%20house%20and%20she%20was%20told%20to%20wait%20in%20the%20drawing%20room.%20She%20waited.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20staff%20came%20and%20told%20Swati%20Maliwal%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20coming%20to%20meet%20her.%20Suddenly%2C%20the%20personal%20secretary%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%2C%20barged%20into%20the%20room.%20Swati%20Maliwal%20said%20he%20started%20screaming%20at%20her%20without%20provocation%20and%20abusing%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20she%20was%20stunned%20by%20the%20sudden%20attack%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20stop.%20She%20also%20urged%20him%20to%20call%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20allegedly%20kept%20shouting%20at%20her%2C%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20authority%20she%20had%20to%20question%20him%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20alleges%20that%20he%20started%20slapping%20her%20and%20%26quot%3Bslapped%20her%207-8%20times%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20she%20kept%20screaming.%20Ms%20Maliwal%20says%20she%20felt%20numb%20and%20shocked%20and%20screamed%20for%20help%20over%20and%20over%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20protect%20herself%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20allegedly%20pushed%20Kumar%20away%20with%20her%20legs.%20She%20alleges%20that%20