TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taj%20Mahal%20Gets%20Competition%20As%20New%20White%20Marble%20Marvel%20Opens%20In%20Agra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20new%20white%20marble%20structure%20in%20Agra%20that%20took%20104%20years%20to%20build%20is%20daily%20drawing%20hordes%20of%20spiritually%20inclined%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visitors%20often%20draw%20comparisons%20between%20the%20iconic%20Taj%20Mahal%20and%20the%20newly%20built%20mausoleum%20of%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Radhasoami%20sect%20in%20Soami%20Bagh%2C%20located%20about%2012%20km%20away%20from%20the%20Taj%20Mahal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immaculate%20white%20marble%20structure%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20attraction%20for%20tourists%20exploring%20Agra.%20Many%20are%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20grandeur%20of%20the%20mausoleum%20and%20consider%20it%20a%20worthy%20rival%20to%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20architectural%20splendour%20of%20the%20city%20known%20for%20its%20Mughal-era%20monuments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%2C%20which%20was%20completed%20in%2022%20years%20with%20the%20labour%20of%20thousands%20of%20skilled%20artisans%20and%20craftsmen%20in%20the%2017th%20century%20under%20a%20medieval%20authoritarian%20regime%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Soami%20Bagh%20mausoleum%20spanned%20over%20a%20century.%20in%20an%20open%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20devoted%20follower%20of%20the%20faith%2C%20Pramod%20Kumar%20mentioned%20that%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20mausoleum%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20unwavering%20faith%2C%20fervour%2C%20and%20dedication%20of%20its%20creators%2C%20who%20were%20driven%20by%20their%20religious%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResting%20on%20a%20foundation%20of%2052%20wells%2C%20the%20193-foot%20tall%20structure%2C%20all%20in%20white%20marble%20from%20Makrana%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20is%20undoubtedly%20one%20of%20the%20most%20ambitious%20projects%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mausoleum%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Radha%20Soami%20faith%20Param%20Purush%20Pooran%20Dhani%20Swamiji%20Maharaj.%20The%20grand%20mausoleum%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20Soami%20Bagh%20colony%20in%20Agra's%20Dayalbagh%20area.%20Each%20day%20bus%20loads%20of%20tourists%20visit%20the%20mausoleum%20and%20express%20their%20admiration%20and%20awe%20at%20the%20exquisite%20craftsmanship%20on%20display.%20The%20entrance%20is%20free%20while%20the%20photography%20is%20not%20permitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20minor%20additions%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20made.%20One%20can%20see%20scores%20of%20craftsmen%20at%20the%20workshop%20equipped%20with%20huge%20machines%20using%20state-of-the-art%20technology.%20%26quot%3BNow%20of%20course%20we%20have%20huge%20grinders%2C%20cutters%2C%20finishers%2C%20lorries%2C%20lifters%2C%20and%20all%20kinds%20of%20machines%20and%20computer%20technology%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20employed%20to%20advantage%20here%2C%20and%20the%20results%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20connected%20with%20the%20project%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%20visitors%20have%20begun%20comparing%20the%20Soami%20Bagh%20mausoleum%20with%20the%20world%20heritage%20monument%2C%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20which%20draws%20thousands%20of%20tourists%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20daily.%20The%20Taj%20Mahal%20houses%20the%20mausoleum%20of%20Mughal%20Emperor%20Shah%20Jahan%20and%20his%20wife%20Mumtaz%20Mahal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20who%20supervised%20the%20construction%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20form%20of%20worship%20that%20has%20been%20going%20on%20and%20will%20go%20on%20relentlessly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Soami%20Bagh%20mausoleum%20stands%20amidst%20a%20colony%20of%20the%20followers%20of%20the%20Radha%20Soami%20faith.%20The%20faith%20has%20millions%20of%20followers%20in%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20as%20well%20as%20foreign%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20samadh%20was%20a%20simple%20white%20sandstone%20structure.%20In%201904%2C%20work%20began%20on%20a%20new%20design%20by%20an%20architect%20from%20Allahabad.%20Work%20was%20held%20up%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20but%20since%201922%20to%20this%20day%20men%20have%20been%20toiling%20away%2C%20mostly%20by%20hand%2C%20at%20the%20enormous%2C%20highly%20decorated%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20artisans%20work%20with%20intense%20devotion.%20Some%20old%20men%20have%20spent%20all%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20site%2C%20as%20their%20fathers%20and%20grandfathers%20did%20before%20them%2C%20and%20as%20their%20sons%20and%20grandsons%20are%20now%20doing.%20These%20days%20the%20artisans%20have%20some%20machinery%20to%20help%20them%2C%20but%20their%20work%20is%20as%20painstaking%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architectural%20design%20of%20the%20building%20conforms%20to%20no%20particular%20style%2C%20modern%20or%20traditional%2C%20though%20in%20conception%20it%20is%20essentially%20oriental.%20An%20effort%20has%20been%20made%20to%20blend%20a%20variety%20of%20styles%20harmoniously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20sponsors%20of%20Soami%20Bagh%2C%20literally%20the%20'garden%20of%20the%20Lord'%2C%20firmly%20deny%20any%20plans%20of%20rivalling%20the%20Taj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2031.4-foot%20gold-plated%20pinnacle%20is%20taller%20than%20that%20of%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20and%20was%20mounted%20by%20a%20crane%20especially%20called%20from%20Delhi%20for%20this%20highly%20specialised%20job.%20It%20took%20years%20because%20marble%20stones%20of%20the%20desired%20size%20could%20not%20be%20found.%20Most%20of%20the%20marble%20for%20the%20mausoleum%20has%20come%20from%20Makrana%20and%20Jodhpur%20quarries%20in%20Rajasthan.%20The%20variegated%20mosaic%20stone%20is%20from%20Nowshera%20in%20Pakistan.%20Semi-precious%20stones%20for%20inlay%20work%20have%20been%20procured%20from%20riverbeds%20in%20central%20and%20southern%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20process%20faced%20many%20problems%2C%20including%20difficulties%20in%20procuring%20the%20right%20quality%20of%20marble%20although%20quarries%20were%20taken%20on%20lease%20in%20Mount%20Abu%20and%20Udaipur%20areas.%20To%20add%20to%20the%20woes%2C%20construction%20work%20was%20affected%20time%20and%20again%20due%20to%20labour%20shortage%2C%20as%20a%20large%20number%20of%20skilled%20masons%20migrated%20to%20greener%20pastures%20in%20Gulf%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20continues%20to%20remain%20the%20first%20choice%20of%20visitors%20who%20are%20fascinated%20by%20the%20romance%20and%20the%20structural%20grandeur%20of%20the%20imposing%20edifice%2C%20the%20spiritually%20inclined%20are%20turning%20to%20Soami%20Bagh%20which%20is%20both%20an%20architectural%20marvel%20and%20a%20centre%20for%20soul%20healing%20and%20solace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promoters%20of%20the%20project%20consider%20it%20wrong%20to%20compare%20it%20with%20any%20other%20building%2C%20but%20those%20who%20visit%20the%20mausoleum%20continue%20to%20wonder%20whether%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20has%20a%20rival%20in%20Agra.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715935860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ftu9v1u58_soami-bagh-agra-soami-bagh-temple-agra_625x300_17_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fagra-news%2Ftaj-mahal-gets-competition-as-new-white-marble-marvel-opens-in-agra-5681826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20white%20marble%20structure%20in%20Agra%20that%20took%20104%20years%20to%20build%20is%20daily%20drawing%20hordes%20of%20spiritually%20inclined%20tourists.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fagra-news%2Ftaj-mahal-gets-competition-as-new-white-marble-marvel-opens-in-agra-5681826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fagra-news%2Ftaj-mahal-gets-competition-as-new-white-marble-marvel-opens-in-agra-5681826%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fagra-news%2Ftaj-mahal-gets-competition-as-new-white-marble-marvel-opens-in-agra-5681826%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forbes%2030%20Under%2030%20Asia%20List%20Out.%20These%20Indians%20Made%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EForbes%20on%20Thursday%20released%20its%209th%20edition%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B30%20Under%2030%20Asia%26quot%3B%20list%2C%20celebrating%20young%20entrepreneurs%2C%20leaders%2C%20and%20trailblazers%20under%2030%2C%20driving%20innovation%20and%20transforming%20industries%20across%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prestigious%20list%20also%20features%20several%20Indian%20entrepreneurs%20from%20diverse%20sectors%20%E2%80%93%20from%C2%A0technology%20and%20sustainability%20to%20logistics%20and%20fashion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EIndians%20on%20Forbes%2030%20under%2030%20list%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EENTERTAINMENT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavithra%20Chari%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavithra%20Chari%2C%20a%20trained%20singer-composer%2C%20gained%20recognition%20as%20half%20of%20the%20duo%20Shadow%20and%20Light%20with%20Anindo%20Bose.%20Their%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Berklee%20Indian%20Ensemble%20earned%20a%20Grammy%20nomination%20in%202023.%20She%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Anirudh%20Varma%20Collective%2C%20touring%20the%20US%2C%20and%20is%20skilled%20in%20Bharatnatyam%20dance.%20Ms%20Chari%20is%20also%20known%20for%20covering%20film%20hits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArpan%20Kumar%20Chandel%20(King)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20rapper%20Arpan%20Kumar%20Chandel%2C%20also%20known%20as%20King%2C%20became%20known%20worldwide%20when%20Nick%20Jonas%20remixed%20his%20hit%20song%20'Maan%20Meri%20Jaan'.%20Mr%20King%20got%20famous%20on%20MTV%20Hustle%20in%202019%20and%20has%20released%20many%20albums%20since.%20His%20latest%2C%20'New%20Life'%2C%20features%20artists%20like%20Nikhita%20Gandhi%20and%20Gucci%20Mane.%20He's%20also%20Sony%20Audio's%20ambassador%20and%20launched%20his%20fragrance%2C%20Blanko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECONSUMER%20TECHNOLOGY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKush%20Jain%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKush%20Jain%20discovered%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20visually%20impaired%20during%20a%20volunteering%20stint%20at%20a%20Bangalore%20school%20in%202018.%20Motivated%20to%20help%2C%20he%20co-founded%20ORama%20AI.%20Their%20innovative%20solution%2C%20a%20smart%20glove%2C%20helps%20the%20blind%20and%20those%20with%20reduced%20vision%20to%20learn%20Braille.%20The%20glove%20features%20an%20embedded%20camera%20and%20speaker%2C%20tracking%20finger%20movements%20and%20audibly%20identifying%20touched%20Braille%20dots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArth%20Chowdhary%2C%20Deyvant%20Bhardwaj%20and%20Oshi%20Kumari%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArth%20Chowdhary%2C%20Deyvant%20Bhardwaj%20and%20Oshi%20Kumari%20co-founded%20InsideFPV%2C%20an%20Indian%20drone%20startup%2C%20in%202020.%20Their%20main%20product%20is%20an%20easy-to-use%20%26quot%3Bplug-and-fly%26quot%3B%20drone%2C%20unlike%20others%20that%20require%20a%20complex%20setup.%20Based%20in%20Surat%2C%20the%20company%20also%20sells%20drones%20and%20parts%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPranav%20Manpuria%20(Flux%20Auto)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAutonomous%20driving%20startup%20Flux%20Auto%20was%20co-founded%20by%20Pranav%20Manpuria%20in%202017.%20The%20company%20is%20working%20on%20creating%20self-driving%20software%20for%20forklifts%20and%20warehouse%20robots.%20They%20claim%20their%20technology%20can%20easily%20fit%20into%20existing%20systems%20of%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Sreyas%20and%20Gautham%20Maheswaran%20(RACE%20Energy)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20university%20friends%20Arun%20Sreyas%20and%20Gautham%20Maheswaran%20created%20RACE%20Energy.%20Headquartered%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20startup%20specialises%20in%20creating%20swappable%20battery%20packs%20tailored%20for%20the%20popular%20three-wheeled%20auto-rickshaws%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20Jain%20and%20Abhik%20Saha%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20Jain%20and%20Abhik%20Saha%20co-founded%20OnePlay%2C%20a%20cloud%20gaming%20startup%20in%20Mumbai%20in%202019.%20OnePlay%20allows%20users%20to%20play%20popular%20games%20like%20Baldur's%20Gate%203%20and%20Palworld%20across%20multiple%20platforms%20without%20needing%20expensive%20hardware.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EENTERPRISE%20TECHNOLOGY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Aggarwal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Aggarwal%20launched%20Credflow%20in%202019%2C%20offering%20cashflow%20management%20software%20for%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20enterprises.%20The%20platform%20analyses%20business%20data%2C%20sends%20automated%20payment%20reminders%2C%20and%20extends%20credit%20lines%20to%20eligible%20users.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaurav%20Piyush%2C%20Mayank%20Varshney%20and%20Yash%20Sharma%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaurav%20Piyush%2C%20Mayank%20Varshney%20and%20Yash%20Sharma%20came%20together%20to%20establish%20Blitz%2C%20a%20logistics%20startup%2C%20in%202020.%20Based%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20the%20company%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Grow%20Simplee%2C%20specialises%20in%20offering%20same-%20or%20next-day%20delivery%20services%20by%20using%20a%20network%20of%20warehouses%20and%20fulfilment%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20Dadia%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20Dadia%20founded%20AIwrite%20in%202022%2C%20providing%20new%20digital%20software%20for%20India's%20insurance%20sector.%20Based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20startup%20uses%20machine%20learning%20to%20help%20insurance%20companies%20analyze%20risks%20and%20develop%20products%20faster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFINANCE%20AND%20VENTURE%20CAPITAL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAalesh%20Avlani%20(CWC)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAalesh%20Avlani%2C%20a%20Boston%20University%20graduate%2C%20co-founded%20Credit%20Wise%20Capital%20(CWC)%2C%20a%20finance%20company%20specialising%20in%20providing%20loans%20for%20motorcycles.%20Founded%20in%202019%2C%20CWC%20received%20%246%20million%20in%20startup%20funding%20the%20following%20year.%20They%20use%20technology%20like%20a%20WhatsApp%20bot%20to%20quickly%20assess%20creditworthiness%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20with%20no%20credit%20history%20to%20apply%20for%20loans.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrinivas%20Sarkar%20and%20Kushagra%20Manglik%20(Coupl)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrinivas%20Sarkar%20and%20Kushagra%20Manglik%20co-founded%20Coupl%2C%20India's%20bank%20designed%20for%20couples%20of%20all%20types.%20Launched%20in%20early%202022%2C%20the%20startup%20helps%20couples%2C%20irrespective%20of%20marital%20status%20or%20sexual%20orientation%2C%20effectively%20manage%20their%20finances%20with%20joint%20accounts%20and%20linked%20ATM%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAniket%20Damle%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAniket%20Damle%20works%20with%20Blackstone's%20private%20equity%20investment%20team%20in%20Asia%2C%20focusing%20on%20investments%20in%20India's%20healthcare%2C%20consumer%2C%20and%20industrial%20sectors.%20At%20just%2023%20years%20old%2C%20he%20made%20his%20first%20deal%20when%20Blackstone%20collaborated%20with%20Sona%20BLW%20to%20establish%20Sona%20Comstar%2C%20a%20technology%20platform%20company%20focused%20on%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYashvardhan%20Kanoi%20(Alter%20Global)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYashvardhan%20Kanoi%20heads%20investments%20at%20Alter%20Global%2C%20a%20venture%20capital%20firm%20linking%20Silicon%20Valley%20with%20startups%20in%20emerging%20markets.%20Since%202019%2C%20he%20led%20investments%20in%20companies%20across%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20South%20Asia%2C%20and%20Latin%20America%20like%20Ula%2C%20BukuKas%2C%20and%20CoLearn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20Maryada%20(Fello)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20Maryada%20co-founded%20Fello%2C%20a%20fintech%20startup%20based%20in%20India.%20Fello%20offers%20rewards%20to%20users%20to%20make%20investing%20enjoyable.%20When%20users%20invest%20a%20certain%20amount%20through%20the%20app%2C%20they%20receive%20a%20ticket%20to%20play%20in-house%20games%20and%20win%20rewards%20and%20prizes.%20Founded%20in%202021%2C%20Fello%20has%20been%20downloaded%20over%20a%20million%20times%20and%20has%20raised%20over%20%245%20million%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnuj%20Srivastava%20and%20Priyesh%20Srivastava%20(OnFinance%20AI)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnuj%20Srivastava%20and%20Priyesh%20Srivastava%20(not%20related)%20co-founded%20OnFinance%20AI%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20startup.%20They%20developed%20NeoGPT%2C%20a%20ChatGPT-like%20service%20tailored%20for%20the%20finance%20industry%2C%20which%20helps%20analyse%20data%2C%20generate%20forecasts%2C%20and%20conduct%20financial%20market%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHEALTHCARE%20AND%20SCIENCE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Ahuja%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20research%20scientist%20Karan%20Ahuja%20will%20become%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20computer%20science%20at%20Northwestern%20University%20starting%20in%20September%202024.%20With%20a%20PhD%20in%20human-computer%20interaction%20from%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%2C%20Mr%20Ahuja%20has%20focused%20on%20projects%20like%20body-movement%20sensing%20for%20smartwatches%20and%20gaze-tracking%20for%20smartphone%20control.%20His%20work%20has%20earned%20nearly%201%2C000%20citations%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAryan%20Chauhan%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAryan%20Chauhan%2C%20along%20with%20his%20mother%20Monika%20Chauhan%2C%20co-founded%20Zivov%20in%202021%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20helping%20with%20diabetes%20treatment.%20Their%20solution%20involves%20a%20self-developed%20sensor%20that%20attaches%20to%20the%20skin%20to%20monitor%20blood%20sugar%20levels.%20Users%20can%20access%20the%20results%20through%20Zivov's%20smartphone%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDUSTRY%2C%20MANUFACTURING%20AND%20ENERGY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshit%20Bansal%20and%20Raghav%20Arora%20(Statiq)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshit%20Bansal%2C%20CEO%20of%20Statiq%2C%20got%20the%20idea%20for%20greener%20transportation%20while%20biking%20through%20Bengaluru's%20polluted%20streets.%20After%20a%20failed%20car-sharing%20venture%20with%20his%20friend%20Raghav%20Arora%2C%20they%20shifted%20their%20focus%20to%20electric%20vehicles.%20Their%20Gurgaon-based%20company%2C%20Statiq%2C%20now%20operates%20a%20nationwide%20network%20of%20charging%20stations%20for%20electric%20cars%2C%20buses%2C%20trucks%2C%20and%20three-wheelers.%20The%20company%20has%20raised%20%2427.5%20million%20from%20investors%20and%20expects%20to%20post%20its%20first%20operating%20profit%20in%20the%20next%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20Jain%20and%20Narayan%20Lal%20Gurjar%20(EF%20Polymer)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20Jain%20and%20Narayan%20Lal%20Gurjar%20co-founded%20the%20agriculture%20startup%20EF%20Polymer%20in%202018.%20Their%20company%20has%20created%20a%20powder-like%20water-retention%20product%20made%20from%20biodegradable%20materials%20like%20bananas%20and%20orange%20peels.%20This%20product%20helps%20retain%20moisture%20in%20the%20soil%20and%20enhance%20crop%20yields%20by%20absorbing%20excess%20water%20and%20gradually%20releasing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Jain%20and%20Rama%20Krishna%20Mendu%20(EndureAir%20Systems)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Jain%20and%20Rama%20Krishna%20Mendu%20founded%20EndureAir%20Systems%2C%20a%20drone%20startup%2C%20in%202018.%20The%20Noida-based%20company%20has%20created%20three%20drone%20models%20for%20mapping%2C%20monitoring%2C%20and%20logistics.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20battery-powered%20and%20can%20carry%20up%20to%2015%20kg%20while%20travelling%2015%20km.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp