findia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fbyeon-woo-seoks-past-modeling-photos-leave-netizens-stunned-by-dramatic-transformation%2Farticleshow%2F110202118.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110202118.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EByeon%20Woo%20Seok's%20popularity%20skyrockets%20with%20'Lovely%20Runner'.%20His%20Weverse%20account%20receives%20100%2C000%20sign-ups%20in%202%20hours.%20Fans%20are%20amazed%20by%20his%20transformation%20and%20discuss%20his%20modeling%20work%20for%20MUSINSA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSlapped%207-8%20Times%2C%20Kicked%20In%20Chest%2C%20Stomach%26quot%3B%3A%20Swati%20Maliwal%20In%20FIR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESlapped%2C%20dragged%20and%20kicked%20in%20the%20chest%20-%20AAP%20leader%20Swati%20Maliwal's%20complaint%20against%20Bibhav%20Kumar%2C%20an%20aide%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20raises%20serious%20charges%20of%20assault.%20Ms%20Maliwal%20claims%20that%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20she%20was%20assaulted%20by%20Mr%20Kumar%20in%20the%20drawing%20room%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20official%20residence%2C%20with%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20present%20in%20the%20house%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20FIR%20filed%20last%20night%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20said%20she%20arrived%20at%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20home%20at%206%2C%20Flag%20Staff%20Road%2C%20Civil%20Lines%20and%20attempted%20to%20contact%20the%20chief%20minister's%20aide%20but%20received%20no%20response.%20She%20said%20she%20informed%20the%20staff%20of%20her%20presence%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20wait%20in%20the%20drawing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20while%20she%20was%20waiting%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20burst%20into%20the%20room%20and%20st