ngage%20in%20combat%20during%20the%20holy%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aajtak.in%2Fworld%2Fstory%2Fpm-modi-says-sent-special-envoy-to-israel-to-ask-him-to-stop-bombarding-in-gaza-during-ramadan-tlifwr-1945693-2024-05-17%5C%22%3EAaj%20Tak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20his%20envoy%20told%20Israel%20they%20should%20not%20bomb%20Gaza%2C%20at%20least%20during%20the%20auspicious%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20month%20of%20Ramzan%2C%20I%20sent%20my%20special%20envoy%20to%20Israel%20to%20meet%20and%20explain%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20(Benjamin%20Netanyahu)%20that%20he%20should%20not%20carry%20out%20bombings%20in%20Gaza%20during%20Ramzan.%20They%20made%20every%20effort%20to%20follow%20it%2C%20but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20there%20was%20a%20fight%20for%202-3%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20publicise%20such%20things%20even%20though%20people%20in%20India%20keep%20%26quot%3Bcornering%20him%20on%20the%20Muslims%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20some%20other%20countries%20also%20tried%20to%20speak%20to%20Israel%20to%20halt%20the%20bombings%20and%20may%20have%20also%20achieved%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20may%20have%20got%20the%20results%20too.%20I%20also%20tried%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%20broke%20out%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20on%20southern%20Israel%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20more%20than%201%2C170%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20retaliation%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2035%2C233%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20Hamas-ruled%20Gaza.%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20says%20that%20the%20assault%20will%20continue%20till%20Hamas%20has%20been%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20said%20that%20he%20made%20standalone%20visits%20to%20both%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%2C%20unlike%20earlier%20governments%20which%20used%20to%20display%20token%20secularism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20fashion%20earlier%20that%20if%20one%20has%20to%20go%20to%20Israel%2C%20a%20visit%20to%20Palestine%20is%20a%20must.%20Do%20secularism%20and%20come%20back.%20But%20I%20refused%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20recounted%20an%20episode%20when%20he%20needed%20to%20travel%20to%20Palestine%20via%20Jordan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20President%20of%20Jordan%2C%20who%20is%20a%20direct%20descendent%20of%20Prophet%20Muhammad%2C%20came%20to%20know%20that%20I%20am%20going%20to%20Palestine%20over%20(the%20airspace%20of%20Jordan)%2C%20he%20told%20me%20'Modi%20ji%2C%20you%20cannot%20go%20like%20this.%20You%20are%20my%20guest%20and%20will%20use%20my%20helicopter'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20unique%20amalgamation%20of%20circumstances%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20his%20home%20for%20dinner%2C%20but%20the%20helicopter%20was%20of%20Jordan%2C%20the%20destination%20was%20Palestine%2C%20and%20I%20was%20escorted%20by%20Israeli%20flight%20attendants.%20All%20three%20are%20different%20but%20for%20Modi%2C%20all%20came%20together%20in%20the%20sky.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715930160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmqk5apg4_narendra-modi_625x300_17_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasked-israel-to-stop-war-in-gaza-during-ramzan-pm-modi-5682868%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20revealed%20that%20India%20sent%20an%20envoy%20to%20Israel%20urging%20them%20to%20stop%20the%20airstrike%20in%20Gaza%20during%20Ramadan.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20urged%20Israel%20to%20mainta