sh-vs-csk-5679945%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fits-going-to-be-ms-dhoni-show-rcb-sent-blunt-warning-ahead-of-do-or-die-ipl-2024-clash-vs-csk-5679945%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20Super-Rich%20Club%20Has%2015%20Members%20With%20Fortunes%20Over%20%24100%20Billion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20super-rich%20club%20now%20has%2015%20members%20with%20fortunes%20over%20%24100%20billion%2C%20the%20most%20on%20record%2C%20as%20they%20ride%20the%20waves%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20luxury%20goods%20and%20geopolitical%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combined%20net%20worth%20for%20these%20people%20is%20up%2013%25%20this%20year%20to%20%242.2%20trillion%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%2C%20beating%20the%20pace%20of%20inflation%20and%20the%20broader%20stock%20market.%20Between%20them%2C%20they%20hold%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20wealth%20of%20the%20world's%20500%20richest%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%2015%20have%20crossed%20%24100%20billion%20before%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20all%20of%20them%20have%20held%20fortunes%20of%20that%20size%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20L'Oreal%20SA%20heiress%20Francoise%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%2C%20Dell%20Technologies%20Inc.%20founder%20Michael%20Dell%20and%20Mexican%20billionaire%20Carlos%20Slim%20all%20initially%20reached%20the%20threshold%20in%20the%20past%20five%20months%20and%20some%20have%20fluctuated%20around%20that%20level%2C%20crossing%20it%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBettencourt%20Meyers%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20amass%20a%2012-figure%20fortune%20in%20December%20after%20shares%20of%20the%20luxury%20cosmetics%20company%20posted%20their%20best%20year%20since%201998.%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%2C%2070%2C%20ranks%2014th%20on%20the%20index%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24101%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDell%2C%2059%2C%20also%20recently%20saw%20his%20wealth%20crest%20the%20%24100%20billion%20mark%20after%20demand%20for%20AI-related%20equipment%20boosted%20Dell%20Technologies'%20share%20price%20to%20record%20highs.%20He's%20now%2011th%20on%20Bloomberg's%20wealth%20index%20with%20a%20fortune%20of%20%24113%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20new%20joiners%20include%20Slim%2C%2084%2C%20who%20ranks%2013th%20with%20%24106%20billion.%20The%20richest%20person%20in%20Latin%20America%20added%20about%20%2428%20billion%20to%20his%20net%20worth%20in%202023%20amid%20a%20boom%20in%20the%20Mexican%20peso%20that's%20helped%20to%20boost%20the%20stock%20of%20companies%20in%20his%20business%20empire%2C%20which%20range%20from%20construction%20to%20operating%20restaurants%20and%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20old%20names%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20club.%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%2061%2C%20recently%20returned%20to%20the%20elite%20group%20after%20a%20short-seller%20attack%20caused%20him%20to%20lose%20more%20wealth%20than%20anyone%20in%202023.%20Shares%20of%20his%20flagship%20Adani%20Enterprises%20Ltd.%20rose%20as%20global%20investors%20increasingly%20focus%20on%20India%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20the%20pack%20is%20LVMH%20founder%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Bernard%20Arnault%2C%2075%2C%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24222%20billion.%20He%20derives%20most%20of%20his%20wealth%20from%20his%20stake%20in%20the%20world's%20largest%20luxury-good%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon.com%20Inc%20founder%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%2060%2C%20ranks%20second%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24208%20billion%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20ownership%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20online%20retailer.%20Tesla%20Inc.%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%2052%2C%20has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24187%20billion%20and%20ranks%20the%20third%20on%20the%20index.%20His%20wealth%2C%20which%20has%20fallen%20by%20more%20than%20%2440%20billion%20this%20year%2C%20mainly%20consists%20of%20his%20stake%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20car%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(